    <item>
      <title>贝莱德称特朗普集会上的枪手出现在公司广告中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/blackrock-says-gunman-from-trump-rally-appeared-in-firm-s-ad</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德公司周日表示，在宾夕法尼亚州集会上枪杀前总统唐纳德·特朗普的 20 岁枪手托马斯·马修·克鲁克斯 (Thomas Matthew Crooks) 曾短暂出现在贝莱德公司的广告中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/blackrock-says-gunman-from-trump-rally-appeared-in-firm-s-ad</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 23:01:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2024 年英国房屋卖家首次下调要价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/uk-home-sellers-cut-asking-prices-for-the-first-time-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于大选的不确定性和居高不下的抵押贷款利率抑制了信心，英国房屋卖家今年首次下调了房产要价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/uk-home-sellers-cut-asking-prices-for-the-first-time-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元上涨，债券期货因特朗普获胜押注而下跌：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/us-futures-waver-as-traders-juggle-trump-win-bets-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在遭遇暗杀后，交易员们对唐纳德·特朗普赢得美国总统大选的可能性进行了评估，美元上涨，美国国债期货下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/us-futures-waver-as-traders-juggle-trump-win-bets-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 22:18:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球市场在反弹后“特朗普交易”增多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/global-markets-ramp-up-the-trump-trade-after-rally-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普遇刺未遂之后，随着世界金融市场开始重新开放，有一件事似乎是可能的：特朗普的交易将获得更大的动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/global-markets-ramp-up-the-trump-trade-after-rally-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普遭攻击后比特币涨至一周多高点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/bitcoin-btc-rises-as-trump-rally-shooting-seen-increasing-re-election-odds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普对暗杀企图做出的坚决回应引发了人们对这位支持加密货币的前总统连任机会上升的猜测，随后比特币触及 61,000 美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/bitcoin-btc-rises-as-trump-rally-shooting-seen-increasing-re-election-odds</guid>
